cdata.name: Hive
cdata.desc: Based in Estonia with roots in Japan,Blockhive creates practical and innovative solutions for businesses in the form of partnership, helping them unlock new markets and untapped opportunities as part of our ambition to create a win-win outcome.Blockhive works with partners to design their blockchain strategy, and jointly develops projects with them. No fees are charged. Instead, revenue from the projects is shared between blockhive and its partners. HIVE is anERC20 token based on the Ethereum network which give Creditors who provided lending to the company the ability to trade their rights with others.
